notes.body: This is an example note. It contains **Markdown**!

notes.title: Make a thing
notes.body: It\'s very easy to make some words **bold** and other words *italic* with\n    Markdown. You can even [link to React\'s website!](https://www.reactjs.org).

notes.title: A note with a very long title because sometimes you need more words
notes.body: You can write all kinds of [amazing](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Amazing)\n    notes in this app! These note live on the server in the `notes` folder.\n    ![This app is powered by React](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/React_Native_Logo.png/800px-React_Native_Logo.png)
